reviewText: It is not as interesting as I thought it would be. I was hoping for something more technical and scholarly.
I saw this on tv and it is powerful and informative worth watching again.
Good teaching program about Isaiah 53, you will learn more about the prophecy about Jesus' first coming through the eyes of His people, the jews!

Great if your are preparing for a debate or conversation with a Jew in order to try to convert, but not particularly useful for a general study of Isaiah 53.  The discussion was interesting but not what the promotional materials indicated.
I was looking more for a movie.  This was more a documentary.

NOt as expected. nothing like Jewish culture or Jewish participants in the panel.
the leader tried very hard though, the teaching is missing that essential Jewish ingredient.
